# 🤖 FES Chatbot API (RAG + SSE)

A FastAPI-based backend powering the **FES Chatbot**, combining **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)** with **OpenAI GPT** for smart, context-aware responses.
Built for scalability, rate-limiting, and protection against scraping or abusive requests.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
app/
├── core/
│   ├── config.py              # Loads env vars, initializes Pinecone index
│   ├── cors.py                # Handles CORS setup
│   ├── rate_limit.py          # Defines rate limiter and handler logic
│   ├── logging_config.py      # Centralized logger configuration
│
├── models/
│   └── schemas.py             # Pydantic models for API requests/responses
│
├── routers/
│   └── chat_router.py         # Core chat endpoints (/chat, /stream)
│
├── services/
│   ├── openai_service.py      # Generates responses using OpenAI GPT models
│   ├── rag_service.py         # Builds RAG context and runs document retrieval
│   └── pinecone_service.py    # Handles Pinecone vector search (queries index and returns matches)
│
├── utils/
│   └── contact_utils.py       # Detects and handles contact-related queries
│
├── main.py                    # Entry point — FastAPI app setup
│
└── __init__.py
```

