## 🧪 Testing

### 1️⃣ Run the Server

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

### 2️⃣ Health Check

```bash
curl -X GET "http://127.0.0.1:8000/health"
```

### 3️⃣ Chat Endpoint

```bash
curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat" ^
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" ^
  -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0" ^
  -d "{\"query\": \"Tell me about FES Lahore branch.\"}"
```

### 4️⃣ Test Rate Limiting (Run multiple times quickly)

```bash
for /l %i in (1,1,10) do curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat" ^
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" ^
  -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0" ^
  -d "{\"query\": \"hi\"}"
```

You’ll eventually get:

```json
{"detail": "Too many requests. Please try again later."}
```

